title: Pressed to choose sides on Ukraine, China trade favors the West - Reuters
content: Pressed to choose sides on Ukraine, China trade favors the West  ReutersView Full Coverage on Google News
description: U.S. President Joe Biden's warning of "consequences" for any aid China may give to Russia's Ukraine war effort could force Chinese President Xi Jinping to choose between a longstanding lucrative trade relationship with the West and a growing strategic partnership with Moscow.
